textfsm_template:
Value PORT (\S+)
Value TRANSCEIVER_TYPE (\S.*\S)
Value PRODUCT_IDENTIFIER (\S+)
Value VENDOR (\S+)
Value SERIAL_NUMBER (\S+)
Value PART_NUMBER (\S+)
Value REV (\S+)
Value TEMPERATURE (\d+\.\d+C)
Value VOLTAGE (\d+\.\d+V)

Start
  ^Port\s+Transceiver Type\s+Product Identifier\s+Vendor\s+Serial Number\s+Part Number\s+Rev\s+Temperature\s+Voltage\s*$$
  ^\s*${PORT}\s+${TRANSCEIVER_TYPE}\s+${PRODUCT_IDENTIFIER}\s+${VENDOR}\s+${SERIAL_NUMBER}\s+${PART_NUMBER}\s+${REV}\s+${TEMPERATURE}\s+${VOLTAGE}\s*$$ -> Record
